node_7.subject: Maria Lopez
node_7.description: This is Maria Lopez's plan for Monday February 13: wake up and complete the morning routine at 2:00 am, get ready and head out to Oak Hill College for her physics classes from 11:30 am to 3:00 pm, have a lunch at 12:00 pm at Hobbs Cafe, go back to her apartment and stream on Twitch from 3:30 pm to 6:00 pm, eat dinner at 6:00 pm, spend some time exploring new ideas from 6:30 pm to 7:30 pm, watch TV from 7:30 to 8:30 pm.
